### Budget Management
@baseUrl = https://cost-katana-backend.store/api
@apiKey = your_api_key

### Create Budget
POST {{baseUrl}}/budget
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "Monthly Budget", "limit": 1000, "period": "monthly"}

### List Budgets
GET {{baseUrl}}/budget
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Get Budget Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/budget/{{budgetId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
